data.description: Don't miss out on this charming Caldwell home with a great location!. Many features that include 2 spacious living areas, vaulted ceilings, new updated paint inside, updated bathrooms as well as updated flooring throughout the home. Laundry room is conveniently located right off the garage that also includes gas hookups. Lots of room for your toys with a 3 car garage, epoxy flooring and additional storage room inside the 3rd bay. RV parking is a huge plus with ample amount of room on each side of the home that can be used as garden space or for more storage. New AC in 2023 and new roof in 2021. Quiet community with no backyard neighbors. Close to all the local amenities, school, shopping, medical care and freeway access.
